 "remarks": "Welcome home to this charming second-floor apartment in a beautifully maintained 1929 Colonial. Offering a thoughtfully designed living space that feels large, this inviting one bedroom home blends timeless character with modern updates. The rental unit features one spacious bedroom, as well as a good sized dedicated office space, an updated kitchen and a brand new remodeled bathroom. Natural light fills the home enhancing it&apos;s warm and welcoming feel. The living room features a cathedral ceiling, skylights and a ceiling fan to make this space feel light and airy. Step outside and enjoy your own private back deck - an ideal spot for morning coffee or relaxing at the end of the day. This unit also has access to a portion of lawn area as well. This is a well cared for home that offers comfort, charm and pride of ownership in a peaceful residential setting. Off-street parking and conveniently located near Route 7, I-95 and Route 15.",
